        <mxCell id="_3SVYA3OFawDS7Pu7LO9-4" value="&lt;strong&gt;Atmospheric Manipulation Initiative (AMI)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Through groundbreaking research conducted by an elite team of scientists and engineers, humanity has developed the &lt;strong&gt;Atmospheric Manipulation System&lt;/strong&gt;, capable of influencing the behavior and effects of asteroids within the atmosphere. To further develop AMI, rare, highly energetic asteroid shards are required, which can be obtained by destroying asteroids." style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
